Titolo: Eternal Filena

Anno: 1995

Descrizione: Eternal Filena (永遠のフィレーナ, Eien no Firēna) is a fantasy light novel series by Takeshi Shudo (best known for writing the scripts for Magical Princess Minky Momo and Pokémon) which was serialized in Japan in Animage, illustrated by Akemi Takada. The series has been collected into nine volumes published by Tokuma Shoten. An OVA series based on the novels was released from 1992 to 1993. The novel series was also adapted into a role-playing video game released by Tokuma Shoten for the Super Famicom in 1995. It was only released commercially in Japan.

